nodes.text: "Mister Browscar" was a male pilot who served in the New Republic during the Galactic Civil War in 5 ABY. He and a fellow pilot named Miss Scowlface picked a fight with the former Imperial Sinjir Rath Velus prior to the Liberation of Kashyyyk. Browscar assaulted Sinjir who left the cantina at the urging of his friend and lover Conder Kyl. However, Sinjir later return and exacted revenge, kocking Browscar unconscious and breaking Scowlface's nose.
